---
title: SuperQuick Scallion Beyond Meat® Noodles with Sesame and Garlic
description: This savoury and flavourful dish features chow mein noodles tossed with tender Beyond Meat® and crisp sugar snap peas. Hoisin and soy sauce add richness and an umami depth to each bite. Quick to prepare and satisfying, this recipe is perfect for a delicious weeknight meal.

